## ðŸ›  Troubleshooting
| Issue | Solution |
|--------|----------|
| Jest not detecting tests | Ensure your test file is in `__tests__/` and named `*.test.js` or `*.spec.js` |
| Tests fail unexpectedly | Run `npx jest --clearCache && npm test` |
| Jest not installed | Run `npm install jest --save-dev` |

